<title>mstḥq kl ạlmjd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mstḥq kl ạlmjd yạ yswʿ
 kl rkbẗ tsjd wạllsạn yʿtrf byk
 mstḥq kl ạlmjd yạ yswʿ
 2- lmạ nyjy nqf qdạmk yạ yswʿ
 kl ʿạly ynḥny kl mhdwm ytbny
 lmạ nyjy nqf qdạmk yạ yswʿ
 3- kẖly ḥḍwrk ymlạ ʿnynạ yạ yswʿ
 ntgẖyr wʿnynạ tsẖwf mjdk bwjh mksẖwf
 kẖly ḥḍwrk ymlạ ʿnynạ yạ yswʿ</lyrics>
